<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ana Sayfa</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        main {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            height: calc(100vh - 150px);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .service-card {
            background-color: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px;
            width: 250px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

            .service-card h2 {
                margin: 0 0 10px;
            }

            .service-card p {
                margin: 0 0 15px;
            }

        .service-info {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        button {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

            button:hover {
                background-color: #45a049;
            }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function redirectToService(serviceType) {
            const name = prompt("Lütfen adınızı girin:");
            if (name) {
                window.location.href = `/transport/${serviceType}/${name}`;
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Ulaşım Servisi</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Taksi Çağır</h2>
            <p>Hızlı ve güvenli taksi çağırma hizmeti.</p>
            <div class="service-info">
                <p><strong>Ücret:</strong> 5 TL/km</p>
                <p><strong>Güzergahlar:</strong> Karaman şehir merkezi</p>
            </div>
            <button onclick="redirectToService('taxi')">Taksi Çağır</button>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
            <h2>Otobüs bileti al</h2>
            <p>Otobüs seferlerini hızlıca çağırın.</p>
            <div class="service-info">
                <p><strong>Ücret:</strong> 2 TL/km</p>
                <p><strong>Güzergahlar:</strong> Karaman - Konya, Karaman - Ermenek, Karaman - Mut</p>
            </div>
            <button onclick="redirectToService('bus')">Otobüs Bileti al</button>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&Powered by Muhammed Mustafa Kurt</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
